Type: Package
Package: ddir
Title: Assess the Clinical Drug-Drug Interaction Risk for Drug Compounds
Version: 0.14.3
Author: Rainer Strotmann
Maintainer: Rainer Strotmann <rainer.strotmann@mailbox.org>
Description: The goal of ddir is to facilitate the analysis of the
